вЂЄ[attendees applauding. cheering]

400
00:21:30.291 --> 00:21:32.083
вЂЄ[thunder rumbling]

401
00:21:34.291 --> 00:21:37.291
вЂЄYou know.
вЂЄGomora. you have a great woman here.

402
00:21:37.375 --> 00:21:39.625
вЂЄ-[Jonas] Mmm.
вЂЄ-[Mr. Msomi] Never forget that.

403
00:21:40.791 --> 00:21:41.958
вЂЄAmen.

404
00:21:42.458 --> 00:21:44.791
вЂЄ[Joyce] Please allow me
вЂЄto walk you to your car.

405
00:21:44.875 --> 00:21:46.708
вЂЄ[Mrs. Msomi chuckles] Certainly.

406
00:21:47.416 --> 00:21:49.000
вЂЄThank you.

407
00:21:49.083 --> 00:21:50.291
вЂЄ-[Mr. Msomi] Okay?
вЂЄ-[Essie] I'm constipated.

408
00:21:50.375 --> 00:21:52.458
вЂЄ-Yeah.
вЂЄ-[Essie] I woke up in the morning.

409
00:21:52.541 --> 00:21:53.541
вЂЄMm-hmm.

410
00:21:54.208 --> 00:21:55.750
вЂЄ-Safe journey. Msomi.
вЂЄ-Thank you.

411
00:21:55.833 --> 00:21:56.833
вЂЄ-[exclaims]
вЂЄ-There you go.

412
00:21:56.916 --> 00:22:00.583
вЂЄ[Essie] Whose car do you think
вЂЄyou're taking? I said. "No way!"

413
00:22:00.666 --> 00:22:03.000
вЂЄI fought!
вЂЄThey don't know who I am. I wentвЂ¦

414
00:22:03.083 --> 00:22:04.958
вЂЄ-Brother.
вЂЄ-[sighs]

415
00:22:05.041 --> 00:22:07.666
вЂЄEssie is embarrassing us

416
00:22:08.250 --> 00:22:09.583
вЂЄin front of our colleagues.

417
00:22:10.166 --> 00:22:11.875
вЂЄ-Sort it out.
вЂЄ-Okay.

418
00:22:12.541 --> 00:22:15.041
вЂЄ-[thunder rumbles]
вЂЄ-[Magesh] Essie. it's time to go home.

419
00:22:15.125 --> 00:22:16.625
вЂЄ[Essie] Why? Why? Why?

420
00:22:16.708 --> 00:22:19.500
вЂЄ-Come on. Hurry up.
вЂЄ-Oh. Magesh. You're such a party pooper.

421
00:22:19.583 --> 00:22:21.666
вЂЄ-You're ruining the vibe.
вЂЄ-There is a lot of alcohol at home.

422
00:22:21.750 --> 00:22:23.333
вЂЄ-Come. Let's go.
вЂЄ-Joyce bought this alcohol

423
00:22:23.416 --> 00:22:25.833
вЂЄ-for us to drink. Why?
вЂЄ-[Magesh] Now. stop there. Let's go.

424
00:22:25.916 --> 00:22:28.750
вЂЄ-[Essie] What's your problem?
вЂЄ-[Matipa] What the hell is going on?

425
00:22:29.625 --> 00:22:34.458
вЂЄThe only reason I came to
вЂЄthis stupid party was to humiliate Joyce.

426
00:22:35.458 --> 00:22:37.625
вЂЄNow it feels like the joke is on me.

427
00:22:37.708 --> 00:22:41.333
вЂЄ[grunts] Do you think this is
вЂЄan appropriate time to talk about this?

428
00:22:41.416 --> 00:22:43.958
вЂЄIs Joyce still going to sign
вЂЄthose divorce papers?

429
00:22:48.833 --> 00:22:50.416
вЂЄJo. I'm talking to you.

430
00:22:51.208 --> 00:22:52.541
вЂЄI'm talking to you.

431
00:22:53.541 --> 00:22:55.125
вЂЄJo. [inhales sharply]

432
00:23:02.666 --> 00:23:03.666
вЂЄ[crickets chirping]

433
00:23:05.416 --> 00:23:06.833
вЂЄ[dog barking]

434
00:23:27.250 --> 00:23:30.916
вЂЄThere was no need for you
вЂЄto drive me all the way home

435
00:23:31.000 --> 00:23:33.208
вЂЄjust to make sure
вЂЄthat I signed your papers.

436
00:24:03.166 --> 00:24:04.166
вЂЄI miss you.

437
00:24:07.000 --> 00:24:08.291
вЂЄI miss you. Joyce.

438
00:24:13.458 --> 00:24:14.666
вЂЄJoвЂ¦ [stammers]

439
00:24:14.750 --> 00:24:16.291
вЂЄI miss you. my love.

440
00:24:23.625 --> 00:24:24.625
вЂЄ[exhales sharply]

441
00:24:29.375 --> 00:24:30.375
вЂЄ[upbeat music playing]

442
00:24:37.541 --> 00:24:39.333
вЂЄ[inhales sharply] JoвЂ¦

443
00:24:45.125 --> 00:24:46.125
вЂЄ[Jonas breathes heavily]

444
00:24:47.833 --> 00:24:49.125
вЂЄ[Joyce moans]
